{"product_id": "368500", "page": 28, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-04", "text": "I briefly summarize the game;\n+Nice Graphic\n+Story\n+Big map (my favorite)\n+Human mechanics\n+Musics\n+Fighting mechanics\n+Nvidia HBAO+ and PCSS+ technology\n-Horse driving mechanism\n-Synchronization with UPlay (the slowest application I've ever seen)\n-No achievement\nThe game has been played on Msi Geforce GTX 1060 (6G Version) with i5 7400,16 gb Ram and Windows 10 Pro.I tried the game on 1920x1080 Ultra High Settings (HBAO+ , PCSS+) easily openned 60 FPS. (Nvidia HBAO+ and PCSS+ really nice tecnology, but it consumes a lot of ram)", "hours": 12.4, "username": "THRE4T", "products": 17, "early_access": false}
