{"product_id": "368500", "page": 30, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-02", "text": "I decided to play this game two years after it's initial release just because I became a skeptic after the disappointing release of Unity. I did love Unity after it's fixes, but there was still alot to do for the game that the developers never accomplished. Now Syndicate has totally changed how I view the franchise. I believe they got right back on track with Assassin's Creed and did well on release. However, I believe there's alot left out due to the yearly release schedule that could've easily been implemented in to the game (such as co-op, more side missions, more DLC, etc.).", "hours": 32.3, "username": "Wonton", "products": 16, "early_access": false}
