{"product_id": "368500", "page": 40, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-08-01", "text": "I'd give this a 6.5/10. i don't like the fact that you only have three main weapons you can use. Past ones there was multitude of weapons and I'd wish they would make a weapons pack that had every weapon possible and have a disclaimer that said these weapons were used in different time periods so noone is confused. Had about six glitches and one crash for the entire game+DLC which is pretty fair for the size of the game. Most of my deaths was caused by climbing difficulty about 13 times. This tittle didn't go far into the story of the ones before.", "hours": 41.0, "user_id": "76561198363064524", "username": "caseyschott", "products": 89, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 40, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-07-31", "text": "This is an Assassin's Creed game, which is the only thing I can be sure about. The graphics and environmental modelling are great. If you are into history and want to walk the street of London in a different time, this surely is the one you should try.\nAs to the story...There is not much to say. Just don't expect yourself to be excited or moved.", "hours": 51.2, "user_id": "76561198209833552", "username": "Warm-blooded Snake", "products": 265, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 40, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-07-31", "text": "I am new to the whole Assassin's Creed games, this is the second one I bought after Black Flag and I am not disapointed. I always wanted to visit London and like history, it was absolutely fascinating to see it all come to life in this game. This game is beautiful and amazing. You quickly grow attached to the characters, not just Jacob and Evie. I loved the grappling hook, making it my favourite mode of transportation. In some mission you could not kill anybody nor be seen without having to flee and it obligated me to use stealth, althought it could be a little frustrating at time, in the end it is some of the missions I remember the most and enjoyed it. I absolutely loved the steath in this game, especially with Evie's chameleon skill. My only con from this game is that sometimes my character jumped on stuff when I did not want him to. It is without a doubt one of my favourite games ever.", "hours": 63.3, "user_id": "76561198262869688", "username": "shao4361", "products": 22, "early_access": false}
