{"product_id": "368500", "page": 54, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-25", "text": "Assassin's Creed Syndicate is currently the perfect form of the new things introduced in Assassin's Creed Unity, and in my opinion, the perfect form of the Assassin's Creed series (at least until they release Origins). Assassin's Creed Syndicate takes everything that was good about previous games, and makes them better, and takes everything that was bad about previous games, and either fixes them, or removes them entirely. If you're a fan of anything from previous Assassin's Creed games, play this one!", "hours": 37.5, "username": "Gun Squared", "products": 361, "early_access": false}
