{"product_id": "368500", "page": 54, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-06-25", "text": "To undestand and compare I have played AC1-2, Brotherhood, Revalations and Black Flag.\nVisually game is awesome, but combat is just sloppy button mash, parkour has been downgraded(no jump options from previous instalations), you stick to all the wrong surfeces. Story is medium, so basically AC standart nowdays. :(\nCustomization is lacking Unity level (one of good few good this in that game), weapon choices are okay.\nSide activities are also okey, but compare to other open-world games, map is empty.\nOverall I would give 6/10 .\nGood buy if on sale and price is under 15 euros, if not, than I would recommend to skip this one.", "hours": 44.4, "user_id": "76561198131137232", "username": "Precious", "products": 20, "early_access": false}
