{"product_id": "368500", "page": 55, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-06-18", "text": "I love the graphics, story, and being able to play a female protaganist, but these two things are making it unplayable:\n* constant crashing with this message:  \"ACS.exe is not working\"\n* when I'm driving a carriage, there's really bad lag and then it crashes (related to first issue I guess)\nVery frustrating.  I guess it doesn't matter how great the story/gameplay is, if you can't play it, so I'm disappointed to say I can't recommend this one.  One would think, after so much time has passed since release, and so many people have been experiencing the same problem, there would have been a fix by now.", "hours": 243.5, "user_id": "76561198155416556", "username": "EasTxRedHead", "products": 26, "early_access": false}
