{"product_id": "368500", "page": 58, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-05-31", "text": "Potential mild spoiler!!!\nLess than 4 hours into the game with a reasonable amount of wandering and exploring I obtained, on a story quest, the most game-breaking device a game of this nature could offer. A grappling hook...\nThe game was playable up until that point with some good features. The story line was as average as I'd expect from AC at this point. The characters were quite boring but just entertaining enough that I would have kept playing...\nUntil the hookshot... That totally killed it for me and I'll have a go at getting my refund please.", "hours": 4.1, "username": "Cerifero", "products": 289, "early_access": false}
