{"product_id": "368500", "page": 74, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-01-31", "text": "Pros\nLondon as a map is great.\nAtmosphere of the game is good.\nHistorical figures were good. (Darwin, Marx etc. )\nOptimization is better than Unity.\nAssassination missions are cool.\nCharacter outfits are nice.\nChanging through Jacob and Evie is nice.\nContrling a gang was good.\nRope launcher was good. London has a lot of building and rope launcher makes it easy to travel and other stuff.\nCons\nThe game is full of bugs and glitches.\nCheap story.\nFreerunning is bad. Unity was way better at freerunning.\nDLCs are rubbish. I played Jack The Ripper and I can say that previous AC DLCs are way better.\nGame is not muliplayer.\nDon't buy this game. It's not worth it. If you want the story, watch it from youtube but this game is not a good game.", "hours": 58.0, "username": "The Sexual Man", "products": 111, "early_access": false}
