{"product_id": "368500", "page": 80, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-01", "text": "Absolutly amazing. Easily the best game I've played for a long time.\nThe free run and graphics in this game are incredable. I see a lot of peole complaining about the controls but if you go through and configure them to the way you like then there's no problem. Yes, the freerun down and action button are the same, but I've found they rarely interfer with eachother. Sometimes I'll have to press a button multiple times for it to work but this is rarely an issue and I can easily overlook it in a game this incredible.\nBUY THIS GAME.", "hours": 39.0, "user_id": "76561198354805664", "username": "zach6215", "products": 18, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 80, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-01", "text": "This is a awesome game, but with one downsite; The Graphics, when you have a good gpu and play on ultra then u will counter low fps, rx 480 8gb xfx edition gets me to around ~min 25,~max 50 fps. So when u want high FPS u should look to a lower setting. Overall now a good game to get for 20 euros", "hours": 37.5, "user_id": "76561198119463645", "username": "Fusti", "products": 17, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
