{"product_id": "368500", "page": 80, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-01", "text": "As an Assassin's Creed Fan and a game developer, I would say that this Syndicate is the best title of the series. Wonderful Graphics, controls, fights. And the most amazing part is the history that makes you feel like you are living that era in London.\nI never feel addected to a Game like Assassin's Creed especially Syndicate", "hours": 42.6, "user_id": "76561198276438245", "username": "DevSherif", "products": 34, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 81, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-31", "text": "Pros:\nReally huge map.\nStoryline is interesting as there are two characters to play.\nGet to play as GUY and GIRL. (Wow. TWO in one!)\nCons:\nYour horse and his carriage is a tank. You cannot die.\nControls feel really clunky, difficult to move about compared to AC3 and AC:BF\nGet to play as GUY and GIRL. (boo. You'll have to focus on TWO skill trees, TWO equipment customisation. This is terrible as I will tend to research fully before customising and this totally makes it so frustrating for some reason.)\nOverall:\nI will play this game if it's on sale and less than SGD 20.\nIf you're looking for a good AC game, Try ASSASSIN'S CREED: BLACK FLAG. Pirates. That's it.", "hours": 4.4, "username": "DawnOfTheSky", "products": 82, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 81, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-31", "text": "It was an ok game, the main story was shorter than AC Unity at about 14-15 hours so that was disapointing. In all honestly I prefered Unity's story as at some points it was pretty boring. Overall though, it was fun and capturing all the Boroughs can add hours to the overall gameplay and are a fun addition. I give it 7.5 child labours out of 10 indutrial revolutions. Also the grappling hook is a blast to play around with.", "hours": 21.4, "user_id": "76561198071696638", "username": "Bismarck", "products": 90, "early_access": false}
