{"product_id": "368500", "page": 86, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-25", "text": "Loving this game! I couldn't get into the previous AC games as much anymore after the Ezio trilogy. But this one is my second favorite after Ezio. I love Jacob and Evie, they're great with a more in depth storyline. The city looks beautiful, the story is interesting, I'd say this one was definitely worth my money. The only minus point I can mention is that after a year there are still some problems. The game crashed quite a few times on me after every cinematic but after sequence 3 or so that didn't happy anymore. Apart from that, I'm addicted and absolutely not disappointed. Would love to see more of Jacob and Evie!", "hours": 148.8, "username": "Falexys", "products": 25, "early_access": false}
