{"product_id": "368500", "page": 87, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-24", "text": "IMO, this is the best AC out there. I'm a PC player and to me its not about how many buttons you can push. Most of the other AC games are heavy button pushing. If you're going to do a PC game keep it around the W,A,S,D keys. I don't like to over reach for keys like P, L or F5 etc...", "hours": 41.9, "user_id": "76561197970340727", "username": "jkelly19", "products": 277, "early_access": false}
