{"product_id": "368500", "page": 90, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-07", "text": "I am a big fan of the Assassin's Creed series. I have enjoyed this game so far but I can't really get into it like I did the previous episodes. I've restarted at least three times but can't quite get hooked. That said, the controls are fantastic and the combat is amazing. I recommend this for fans of \u2665\u2665\u2665 Creed, and players that just like shanking people.", "hours": 89.8, "compensation": "Product received for free", "username": "Rekkles #Acc4Sell", "products": 88, "found_funny": 3, "early_access": false}
