{"product_id": "368500", "page": 105, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-10-18", "text": "A return to form for Ubisoft.\nI have played every Assassin's creed since Assassin's creed 2 (excluding Unity)\nA very enjoyable game with comedy, wit and plenty of action. A few bugs here and there but nothing like the reports from Unity XD. Ropelauncher is very useful and the Rooks is a new take on the Brotherhood of olf. Would've liked an overhauled parkour system (Mirror's edge/Dying light) but had everything an Assassin's Creed game should have\n10/10 :)", "hours": 79.6, "username": "originalClown", "products": 61, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
