{"product_id": "368500", "page": 108, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-30", "text": "As far as mechanics go, it's not very realistic, but boy is it fun and EASY to move around. I really enjoyed the storyline. Jacob and Evie and my two favorite assassins behind Altair. They're fun, they joke with each other, but they're also badass and get things done. This game is probably one of the best AC games yet, and I'm sooo excited to see another. I've been following the series since the first game. I REALLY want to see the next games similar to this one. The graphics ARE SO AMAZING. Unfortunately my computer can't handle ultra graphics, but even on high graphics, I'm blown away.", "hours": 97.4, "username": "vicarious.erosion.420", "products": 8, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 108, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-28", "text": "I really enjoyed this game nice combat system, free running.  Play all the AC game and I can say this is  atleasts 3x better then unity.", "hours": 33.2, "username": "M3ndoza!*", "products": 496, "early_access": false}
