{"product_id": "368500", "page": 110, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-16", "text": "You smash people with a horse and buggy, swing between buildings with a grappling hook, Victorian London is literally your playground. The story is relatively simple yet the character development is fantastic. Eve and Mr. Green are wonderful, and Jacob is a total \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665. The other NPCs also have great personality and it's simply a joy to do quests with them and learn a bit about them. I also highly recommend the Jack the Ripper DLC, it's a cool continuation of the story of the characters while adding a surprisingly dark brutal element to the game.", "hours": 74.0, "user_id": "76561197972052979", "username": "knapster2k", "products": 185, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
