{"product_id": "368500", "page": 111, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-09", "text": "Assassin's Creed Syndicate or as I like to call it Saints row in disguise. lets get one thing strate first it's not an Assassin's creed but never the less it's still a good game.\nBasics:\nYou play as Jacob and Evie Frye, gang leaders of there new gang thay made on the spot called the rooks much like the rooks from chess <--that was a joke. You can upgrand your rooks buy spending money and crafting materials that you can find, earn or steal. You can upgrand Jacob and Evie with skill points and new weapons and armor ya they added a level up system in the game for better or worse.\nGamePlay:\nThe Gameplay is fun you can sneak you can go in load (as load as you acn go with a sword) or you can run people over with a carriage and some how not get dsynchronize. I guess the hours did it??? Any way it's fun.\nPerformance:\nPerformance sucks you need like tripple or perhaps even more of the speacs to play this game smothly and it gos through ubisoft so that may be way also that means max frame rate of 60pfs because of ubisoft.\nStory:\nIt's good lets leave it at that don't wont to spoil it for ya.\nExtra:\nI own this game for the PS4 and I like to play it on there over my pc just saying btw I have a pc that can play day z on ultra but can't play this game I mean come on!!! Not to menchin it took me a bit to figure out why it would not run in the first place forgot what I did but if I remember I'll post it in other words it may not start up for you as well after waiting like 5 hours for it to download so be aware.\nSo YAY fo console NAA for PC (I'm a pc gamer so don't get me wrong.)", "hours": 16.2, "user_id": "76561198114548108", "username": "MindlessKiller27", "products": 124, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "368500", "page": 111, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-09-09", "text": "Amazing game!\nFirst time i saw the reviews for this game, i thought it's not worth it, but apperently, the reviews aren't really helpful (at least for me).\nThis game is totally playable, as i saw many guys saying that it's not, but i could run it on high sittings with a decent pc, not that good, but i could run it on a decent fps.\nThe story-line of this game is good, but it's not the best on the serie. but the graphics, music and the map, i find them the best.\nA special thanks to the devs and i hope the next Assassin's creed game will be awsome. ^_^", "hours": 23.2, "username": "RarE^", "products": 557, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
