{"product_id": "368500", "page": 112, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-31", "text": "I'll be honest, I usualy not a big fan of the Assasin's Creed series, but this one cought my attantion.\nFlowing and simple gameplay, a rather Variety set of missions, nice story and good balaced with the fray twins, one for stelth and one for frontal fights. I also liked the leveling system, not too hard but do make you work for your progress and the gang side is a good add, though maybe there was room for more in this aspect.\nI do admit that I incountered some technical issue during the game, but nothing that ruin the gaming expirience.", "hours": 24.7, "user_id": "76561197992852801", "username": "SKiller", "products": 141, "early_access": false}
