{"product_id": "368500", "page": 114, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-14", "text": "After Assassin's Creed III and Unity: \"This was NOT a good experience, I'm never playing another AC game ever again.\"\nAfter Assassin's Creed Syndicate: \"Holy\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 I need to go back and play all those AC games I've missed!\"", "hours": 31.3, "username": "Douglas Kim", "products": 880, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
