{"product_id": "368500", "page": 124, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-02", "text": "My gamer life started with the first Assassin's Creed game. I played each installment up until Black Flag. In this series of games there were some aspects that I valued most of all, especialy in the first four games. From then on i felt the magic of AC had been lost. AC Syndicate became for me a fresh start for this saga, returning most of our beloved AC defining characteristics, such as: immersive story and interesting characters, stealth and fight mechanincs and that feeling that you belong to the historical setting the story takes place.\nAll in all, as a fan of the first AC games, i believe this game is a must for those wishing for the good old AC days. It's not a perfect game, but it is different in a smart and new kind of way. I'd give it 4 stars, in five.", "hours": 45.2, "username": "rykapa", "products": 65, "early_access": false}
