{"product_id": "368500", "page": 139, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-05-06", "text": "+ Awesome graphic, duh!\n- Still get crash from time to time\n+ Can play either one of the 2 MCs most of the time\n+ Really, I can't think any downside of this, their VA are awesome too\n+ HQ in a moving train!\n- HQ in a MOVING train, there's a fast travel, but still\n+ Better mechanics than previous ACs, especially combats\n- I missed Black Flag's ship, yeah, you can't control the train\n+ Lots of crafting items\n- Feels like a pay to win, but not, but yeah, not really, but you know what I mean, Ubisoft\n+ A good amount of new system\n- The NPCs feels more idiotic than ever\nI can't think for anything more, it's AC for christ's sake, whaddya expect? They're starting to be a generic franchise. I say it's better than Black Flag, and definitely way way better than Unity. Buy it? Definitely", "hours": 36.7, "username": "Van Geaux", "products": 254, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
