{"product_id": "368500", "page": 160, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-03-24", "text": "Fun game, Almost on par with Black Flag(Ninja Pirate - not an assassin). I believe they could have done more with the game but all and all I am very happy with my purchase.\nRun's okay with NV surround some FPS drops even running 780TI SLI and 47770k.\nReview Disclaimer\n(I am NOT an Assassin's Creed fan. I am a Black flag, Syndicate, and Rogue Fan).\nI've played AC1, AC2, Brotherhood, AC3 and Unity via rentals these games didn't lure me in or keep my interest enough to play longer than an hour or two max.", "hours": 36.7, "username": "ArieS\u2122", "products": 77, "early_access": false}
