{"product_id": "368500", "page": 173, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-31", "text": "I know, I know, Assassin's Creed has had many entries so far, and most of them have the same feel to them, but if you are a fan, such as myself, or haven't played an Assassin's Creed yet, then this one is a great choice! It is very well ported for PC, and has some very amazing looking textures. I love the setting being in London and the story line is pretty good so far. I do think the Assassin's Creed series needs a revamp and maybe a few new and different features, but either way I do think this is a great game and I have been having a lot of fun playing it so far, and committed to completing it very soon.\nP.S. One thing I do wish it had is Steam achievements. It does have achievements on Uplay, but wish the Devs would add them to Steam as well.", "hours": 28.9, "user_id": "76561198179577294", "username": "v.JohnnyJDM85 \u738b\u5c06", "products": 265, "early_access": false}
