{"product_id": "368500", "page": 180, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-15", "text": "Been a fan of AC series since the first one came out. I won't be like the others who will hate the game because of what happene to Unity. The game has a brilliant new combat system and the appearance of the city is delightful, the story is so interesting that I was sitting at the computer playing without hearing what's going on around me. If I did not have a weak hardware at his disposal, I spent the whole day in this world. Plus points of of this game are;\n+ New combat system\n+ new weapons\n+ New story\n+ Wonderful city full of life\n+ Brilliant side missions with whom I spent more time than the main thread\n+ Able to choose form\n+ Carriages that they can lead\n+ chance to meet historical figures\nHowever, there are also cons\n- The level of the game is easy\n- Opponents are sometimes stupid\n- they killed Jacob on the Jack the Ripper dlc </3 (ooops spoiler alert)", "hours": 50.3, "username": "kenneth2k27", "products": 245, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
