{"product_id": "368500", "page": 199, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-12-28", "text": "BEWARE WINDOWS 10 USERS!!!\nNow that I have your attention, this game won't start. It gets as far as the intro screen (right after it asks you to press a button), goes on for a few seconds, and then crashes. I have been at this for an hour andit is really\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665me off. I read up on it and I am currently attempting a fresh reinstall on my C: drive instead of my D: drive. Apparently it is a common issue with Ubisoft's products that they only work on the C: drive. I will update this review whenever I finish the download (which might be tomrrow. The first install took me 16 hours because of my crappy wifi).\n*UPDATE*\nI'm getting a refund to this game. I've been trying to fix this piece of\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665for three days now. It ran for about a half hour untill I restarted the game, allowing it to crash again.", "hours": 7.0, "username": "PB4000", "products": 115, "early_access": false}
