{"product_id": "368500", "page": 221, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-30", "text": "Just finished the game and I would recommend it.\nThe Good:\nThe Story is good until the end and then sucks.\nThe Bad:\nThe controls are really bad at times.  I do not know how many times my character just all the sudden went nuts and got me killed.\nThe driving of horse drawn carriages in the game is downright horrible.  To the makers of the game go play Red Dead Redemption and learn a thing or two.\nOverall:\nGood story and bad controls, but the game was still fun to play.", "hours": 52.6, "user_id": "76561197970507375", "username": "Squake", "products": 195, "early_access": false}
