{"product_id": "368500", "page": 224, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-11-27", "text": "I wanted to like this, I really did, but the amount of game breaking bugs and crashes made that impossible. When I can run MGS:TPP and Fallout 4 at high settings there is no reason why I shouldn't be able to run this at least at minnimum. Maybe if Ubisoft can fix the issues I would recommend, But until they do don't bother wasting your money.", "hours": 56.9, "username": "SacredFrey", "products": 219, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
