{"product_id": "368500", "page": 248, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-19", "text": "By far the best Assassin's Creed in a long time, possibly one of the best (if not best) in general.\nThe main characters are likeable, the gameplay is a better, more refined version of what it used to be.\nThe new sneaking mechanics and melee system are both more fluid and fun.\nLondon looks incredible, as does fighting on a moving train or carriage. The new driving system is pretty decent as well.\nAnd it actually runs well and isn't a buggy mess.", "hours": 27.6, "username": "Saninsince992", "products": 607, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
