{"product_id": "368500", "page": 250, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-19", "text": "So far the only hitch I got was in the prologue mission when I take out a lot of the guards the game stuttered, got through it and now the game runs silky smooth (maybe the first part just had a problem with the ragdoll physics) definitely way better than Unity's launch\nPrologue issues aside, game runs extremely well for me so far :)", "hours": 59.0, "user_id": "76561198071822725", "username": "SG.Doi_Takki", "products": 123, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
