{"product_id": "368500", "page": 252, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-18", "text": "My first impressions: its pretty, even if you aren't on the max settings; it runs smoothly; and its immediately and noticeably less buggy than Unity was on launch. Furthermore, the story is immediately more captivating.\nIf somebody wants to hate this game because they didn't like Unity, fine, but 20 minutes isn't really enough time to give a comprehensive review. If you like the AC series, try it out.\nThere are probably bugs, but my game didn't break on launch, so this is immediately better.\nIf there are any big, bad bugs, Ubisoft will fix them, just like they did with Unity (which, by the way, turned out to be pretty fun after the bug fixes).", "hours": 17.8, "username": "williad", "products": 310, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
